Package com.genesyslab.platform.clusterprotocol.lb

Load Balancer for Cluster Protocol.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    ClusterProtocolLoadBalancer
    Common interface for Cluster Protocol Load Balancer component.
    ClusterProtocolLoadBalancerFactory
    Cluster Protocol Load Balancer Factory interface.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ClusterNodesShuffler
    Helper component for doing cluster load balancing from client type applications.
    DefaultClusterLoadBalancer
    Default Cluster Protocol Load Balancer.
    It implements simple "round robin" strategy on available cluster nodes.
    DefaultClusterProtocolLoadBalancerFactory
    Default implementation of Cluster Protocol Load Balancer.
